===Noun===
'''fætus''' (''plural'' '''[[fætus’s]]''')

# ''(UK)'' An unborn or unhatched vertebrate whose stem cells have divided to differentiate the primary anatomical systems and features of the mature animal.
# ''(US)'' An unborn or unhatched vertebrate that is showing signs of the mature animal; an unborn baby after the 7th week of gestation.
